(88, 'United Arab Emirates', 'United Arab Emirates', 'United Arab Emirates', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/2406731/pexels-photo-2406731.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Another stunning beauty of the Arab word is the United Arab Emirates with Dubai as its most precious tourist jewel. A hub for international tourists, UAE is found in the bucket lists of several travelers. If you are one of them then this is the year when you can plan a budget international trip and explore the UAE. This land of Sheikhs hides attractions that never fail to inspire awe and blankets experiences that are nothing less than Royal! Dubai is indeed one of the cheapest countries to visit from India.', 23.841924, 54.114509, 50, 5, 50000, 4.1, 0),
(89, 'Hong Kong', 'Hong Kong', 'Hong Kong', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/2861883/pexels-photo-2861883.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'The former British colony perched on the shore of South China Sea offers plenty of bargains despite being famous for its glitz lifestyle. Head here for a groovy and electrifying holiday experience. Hong Kong is one of the best places when thinking of cheap international destinations from India so make sure that you explore it this year if you still haven’t.', 22.319852, 114.169326, 40, 5, 400000, 4.2, 0),
(90, 'Sri Lanka', 'Sri Lanka', 'Sri Lanka', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/739409/pexels-photo-739409.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Sri Lanka is one of the most cheap foreign trips from India. Famous for being the best backpacking destination, it is home to landscapes and culture which is much like India. Visit this home away from home that solves the purpose for those looking forward to cheap foreign trips from India. It is one of the world’s cheapest countries to travel from India. With the fragrance of tea plantations encircling the atmosphere, lush green foliage covering the floors, and locals serving the mouth-watering dishes, Sri Lanka is a destination that takes away the breath of travelers!', 7.595999, 80.699873, 35, 6, 60000, 4.4, 0),
(91, 'Cambodia', 'Cambodia', 'Cambodia', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/1534057/pexels-photo-1534057.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Cambodia is one of the most beautiful yet cheapest international destinations. The enchanting form of cultural heritage, the country of Cambodia will leave you wanting for more with its panoramic and rustic beauty. It is one of the most cheap foreign trips from India.', 12.715269, 104.924154, 25, 2, 10000, 4.5, 0),
(92, 'Vietnam', 'Vietnam', 'Vietnam', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/1660996/pexels-photo-1660996.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Vietnam is indeed one of the best places for budget international trips. Shaped like the letter “S”, lying on the eastern part of Indo-Chinese peninsula is Vietnam. In the country you will find timeless charm, and a flavor of another Asian culture which is why it is one of the best places to visit in March outside India.', 14.498164, 0, 40, 6, 20000, 3.7, 0),
(93, 'Bhutan', 'Bhutan', 'Bhutan', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/4525420/pexels-photo-4525420.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'The scenic country also called as the ‘land of the Thunder Dragons’ or the ‘Druk Yul’, offers pristine untouched natural wonders.This year is full of long weekends and Bhutan is one of the best among the various cheap international destinations from India. Head to on a trip to the Shangri La of Himalayas. It is one of the most cheap foreign trips from India.', 27.409976, 90.425551, 35, 7, 13333, 4.8, 0),
(94, 'Nepal', 'Nepal', 'Nepal', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/1531660/pexels-photo-1531660.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'An ideal holiday destination for all types of traveler, surrounded by lofty peaks and scenic landscapes lays Nepal. It is a beautiful country which is every traveler’s delight and makes way for the globetrotters to embark on one of the best budget international trips under 30k. It is the world’s cheapest countries to travel from India.', 0, 83.947283, 25, 8, 55555, 5, 0),
(95, 'Turkey', 'Turkey', 'Turkey', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/2668314/pexels-photo-2668314.jpeg', 'You think of Turkey and the instant obvious is Istanbul which also makes it the highest famed tourist spots in the world. It is the world’s cheapest foreign tour from India. If you are looking for best budget international trips from india then you can surely plan a trip to Turkey!', 38.892407, 35.437122, 30, 9, 70005, 3.9, 0),
(96, 'Kenya', 'Kenya', 'Kenya', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/1670732/pexels-photo-1670732.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Another destination that offers awesome low budget international trip is Kenya. The first thing that pops up when you think about Kenya is the exorbitant African wildlife and safaris. Moreover, the destination is a perfect pick for wildlife photography.', 0.487078, 37.887836, 30, 4, 600500, 5, 0),
(97, 'Egypt', 'Egypt', 'Egypt', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/5609738/pexels-photo-5609738.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Egypt – the mum-mummy-ia place could offer a vacation for a lifetime. If you still haven’t expored Egypt then grab this chance to plan of the best budget international trips. Whether you are a history buff or an explorer, you would definitely enjoy a few days here.', 26.495772, 29.903917, 40, 3, 255555, 4.9, 0),
(98, 'South Korea', 'South Korea', 'South Korea', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/2246789/pexels-photo-2246789.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'South Korea is another place where you can take budget trips abroad from India. It will impress you with its lush green and hilly countryside, studded with cherry trees, along with the ancient Buddhist temples. The fusion of coastal fishing villages, sub-tropical islands and high-tech cities including the capital, Seoul, together contribute to an amazing low-budget international tour experience.', 36.474609, 127.707337, 40, 6, 233333, 4.8, 0),
(99, 'Myanmar', 'Myanmar', 'Myanmar', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/3560161/pexels-photo-3560161.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Also known as Burma, the country of Myanmar embraces multi ethnicity and culture. Further the scenic beauty of the country will leave you spell bound. So, make sure that you tick of this destination from your bucket list by planning of the budget-friendly international trips.', 21.331922, 96.489866, 35, 5, 455555, 4.6, 0),
(100, 'China', 'China', 'China', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/189833/pexels-photo-189833.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'A giant tourist attracting magnet of the Asian continent is China! It boasts of being the 3rd highest visited country in the world. Plan a foreign tour in low budget and explore China the way you want. Indulge in Chinese delicacies, visit world-class attractions, enjoy a sneak-peek into it’s culture while making the most of your vacation', 35.86166, 104.195396, 40, 2, 100000, 4.2, 0),
(101, 'Taiwan', 'Taiwan', 'Taiwan', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/981147/pexels-photo-981147.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Also known as “Formosa”, the stunning beauty of Taiwan will take you through varied landscapes of artistic buildings, shimmering skyscrapers, luxury resorts, high-rising mountains, and beautiful Chinese temples. Explore all these places by planning one of the best budget international trips this year.', 23.697809, 120.960518, 40, 4, 80000, 4.7, 0),
(102, 'Lebanon', 'Lebanon', 'Lebanon', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/3610377/pexels-photo-3610377.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'With the title of being one of the most ancient countries in the world, Lebanon represents rich history and diversity in its culture. It is one of the best cheap international trips from India. If you still haven’t explored Lebanon then this your chance to plan a budget international trip with your friends or family.', 33.854721, 35.862286, 45, 3, 90000, 4.6, 0),
(103, 'Sultanate Of Oman', 'Sultanate Of Oman', 'Sultanate Of Oman', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/10599258/pexels-photo-10599258.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'The Sultanate of Oman is the cheapest foreign trip from India. Another jewel in the Persian Gulf is, Oman with Muscat at its capital which is famed for being the second best city in the world. It is one of the best budget international trips under 30K.', 23.613541, 58.594109, 30, 5, 70000, 3.7, 0),
(104, 'Russia', 'Russia', 'Russia', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/753339/pexels-photo-753339.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Russia is among the most stunning as well as tourist-friendly destinations in the world. It definitely qualifies for budget friendly international trips from India. And what’s more, its diverse cultures, varied traditions, mouth-watering cuisine makes it an indispensable part of your travel wishlist! In fact, it’s one of the highest visited places in Europe owing to its boundless natural beauty. Make sure that you cover Russia in this year as it is one of the best places to plan cheap international trips', 61.52401, 105.318756, 45, 6, 600000, 3.8, 0),
(105, 'Jordan', 'Jordan', 'Jordan', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/3214958/pexels-photo-3214958.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Jordan isn’t just about open-air museums, ancient ruins, and great skylines. Its happening nightlife and gorgeous beaches also attract travelers from far and wide and the fact that it is one of the cheapest countries to visit from India makes it even more lucrative. The delicious cuisine, warm and friendly people, and unique activities make Jordan an adventure-packed and destination for wanderers steeped in history. The government is developing Jordan as an important center for tourism competing with its neighbors, and it has started contributing tremendously in its economy. So, include Jordan in your list of bugdet international trips and tick off this destination this year.', 30.5852, 36.2384, 30, 4, 705044, 3.9, 1),
(106, 'Paraguay', 'Paraguay', 'South America', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/90597/pexels-photo-90597.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'A less-popular country in the South American continent, Paraguay is what every adventurer dreams of. It is an unconventional choice for budget international trips from India. To give you the exact vibes of an offbeat holiday, this place boasts of a mix of conventional and modern living styles – a place where you’ll see carts and Mercedez standing together. That’s right! With a subtropical forest land like Atlantic in one corner and dense vegetation in Chaco on the other corner, you simply cannot go wrong with this place! Plan a budget foreign trip to Paraguay and explore this place with your loved one, family or friends.', -9.605854, -57.121479, 45, 3, 700000, 4.9, 0),
(107, 'Laos', 'Laos', 'Laos', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/1385474/pexels-photo-1385474.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'If your wanderlust is giving you an itch but your pocket cannot afford any, then there is still one place where you could take a trip without losing much. Plan a low budget international trip to Laos and have an amazing backpacking experience in this South East Asian country. In case your geography is weak, then you should know that Laos shares its borders with Vietnam and Cambodia. It is one of the most stunning yet cheap countries to visit from India.', 19.475655, 102.494562, 30, 3, 70500, 4.4, 0),
(108, 'Japan', 'Japan', 'Japan', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/3408353/pexels-photo-3408353.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'If you are looking for international honeymoon destinations in budget, you could fly to Japan. It is not only beautiful but also culturally rich country where you would get to experience a variety of things. It is the best foreign trip in low budget if you can manage.', 36.26483, 138.157189, 65, 2, 600000, 4.3, 0),
(109, 'Greece', 'Greece', 'Greece', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/161815/santorini-oia-greece-water-161815.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Take a low budget foreign trip to the island of Greece and enjoy Mediterranean landscapes. Greece is one of the most romantic places with its enchanting scenery and what not. If you plan your holiday carefully, you can definitely manage a low budget international trip to Greece.', 39.358723, 22.482662, 50, 6, 200000, 4, 0),
(110, 'Philippines', 'Philippines', 'Philippines', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/1076240/pexels-photo-1076240.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'The list of budget international trips couldn’t be complete without talking about Philippines. Emerald rice fields, water buffaloes, beautiful beaches, graffiti walls and a place where even the fuming volcanoes look pretty, Philippines is made of dreams. You can indulge in canoeing, mountain biking and many other adventure activities here. The place can make you have the cheapest foreign trip from India.', 12.410718, 122.966876, 50, 3, 355550, 3.9, 0),
(111, 'Nicaragua', 'Nicaragua', 'Nicaragua', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/3822541/pexels-photo-3822541.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'As weird as the name might sound, this is one of the best cheap international trips you can take. Imagine a place that is beautifully tucked between two gorgeous countries with a marvellous coastline, that’s Nicargua. Nestled between Costa Rica and Honduras, Nicargua is best desscribed as an unending terrain of lakes and beaches and volcanoes. The place is known for the cheapest foreign tour packages from India.', 12.783198, -85.072632, 42, 4, 10000, 5, 0),
(112, 'Bangladesh', 'Bangladesh', 'Bangladesh', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/122107/pexels-photo-122107.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Planning a cheapest international trip from India? Now we know Bangladesh is not the “go to” destination for everyone but nevertheless its beautiful. If you are looking for places to visit outside India then Bangladesh is worth considering. It is a perfect combination of beautiful and cheap international holidays.', 24.144149, 90.251581, 40, 3, 20000, 3.4, 0),
(113, 'Bolivia', 'Bolivia', 'Bolivia', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/3290069/pexels-photo-3290069.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Well, imagine a destination where natural wonders and which is also one of the cheapest countries to visit from India! Well, that’s Bolivia for you. One of the offbeat countries in South America. If you ask what is the most unique and special things about this country then it is its versatility. We are still wondering how one small country can house mountains, desert and rainforests and even a glass smooth lake.', -16.957261, -64.691949, 35, 9, 50000, 4.1, 0),
(114, 'The Great Barrier Reef', 'Australia', 'Australia', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/6465339/pexels-photo-6465339.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'The Great Barrier Reef is one of the undisputed best vacation spots for anyone who wants the opportunity to glimpse one of the most incredible marvels of nature.', -18.00000488962461, 146.833324, 45, 6, 10000, 4.2, 0),
(115, 'Plitvice Lakes', 'Croatia', 'Croatia', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/14319765/pexels-photo-14319765.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'The Plitvice Lakes can be found on Croatia’s Adriatic Sea coast, just lingering on the border between Zadar and the nation’s capital, Zagreb.', 44.86539, 15.582017, 40, 7, 20000, 4.4, 0),
(116, 'Victoria Falls', 'Zambia/Zimbabwe', 'Zambia/Zimbabwe', 'https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/07/e0/bb/d4/an-angels-view.jpg?w=800&h=-1&s=1', 'Victoria Falls is one of the earth’s largest waterfalls, reaching a majestic 355 feet in height and spanning across an entire mile.', -17.93179, -17.93179, 45, 4, 300000, 4.5, 0),
(117, 'Grand Canyon National Park', 'USA', 'USA', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/4341879/pexels-photo-4341879.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'If you like traveling at all, the Grand Canyon National Park in Arizona is one of the best places to visit.', 36.099781, -112.112587, 50, 5, 50000, 3.7, 0),
(118, 'Bora Bora', 'French Polynesia', 'French Polynesia', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/1188473/pexels-photo-1188473.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Bora Bora is an island paradise isolated from much of the world, in the middle of the South Pacific ocean.', -16.507827, -151.742092, 40, 2, 400000, 4.8, 0),
(119, 'Petra', 'Jordan', 'Jordan', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/720254/pexels-photo-720254.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Petra is an awe-inspiring archaeological site that holds so much history and breathtaking majesty that it is easily one of the best vacation spots in the world.', 30.328439, 35.444359, 35, 3, 60000, 5, 0),
(120, 'Arashiyama Bamboo Grove', 'Japan', 'Japan', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/6160161/pexels-photo-6160161.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'The Arashiyama Bamboo Grove is among the best places to travel in the already attraction-packed nation of Japan.', 35.01682015, 135.671334, 25, 6, 10000, 3.9, 0),
(121, 'Stonehenge', 'England', 'England', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/1448136/pexels-photo-1448136.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Stonehenge is such a mysterious location, which is why it is one of the best places to visit in the world.', 51.178869, -1.825958, 40, 4, 20000, 5, 0),
(122, 'Amalfi Coast', 'Italy', 'Italy', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/3225528/pexels-photo-3225528.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Whether you’re looking for some calm relaxation, you’re itching for some fresh seafood, or you desire something more adventurous, Amalfi Coast is one of the best vacation spots you can hope for.', 40.633342, 14.602942, 35, 6, 13333, 4.9, 0),
(123, 'Machu Picchu', 'Peru', 'Peru', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/2929906/pexels-photo-2929906.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Machu Picchu may have been famous for a long time, but it’s one of the more recently discovered old archaeological ruins, and it’s definitely one of the top best places to travel in the world.', -13.226707, -72.497257, 25, 4, 55555, 4.8, 0),
(124, 'Niagara Falls', 'Canada/USA', 'Canada/USA', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/1486902/pexels-photo-1486902.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'The Niagara Falls, positioned on the border between America and Canada, is a once-in-a-lifetime type of trip that you won’t regret.', 43.08683, -79.088002, 30, 6, 70005, 4.6, 0),
(125, 'Cappadocia', 'Turkey', 'Turkey', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/3889704/pexels-photo-3889704.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'Cappadocia is likely one of the most intriguing vacation spots in the world.This is because of its fascinating, unique, and borderline bizarre natural structures known as fairy chimneys.', 38.729163, 35.292247, 30, 5, 600500, 4.2, 0),
(126, 'Neuschwanstein Castle', 'Germany', 'Germany', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/234311/pexels-photo-234311.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'You may feel like Neuschwanstein Castle looks familiar.That’s because the famed Cinderella’s Castle building, located in Disney World, is heavily inspired by and modeled after this incredible, opulent palace.', 47.55757611, 10.7497983, 40, 7, 255555, 4.7, 0),
(127, 'Marble Caves', 'Argentina/Chile', 'Argentina/Chile', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/14437116/pexels-photo-14437116.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'The Marble Caves are among the best places to visit if you are a fan of unreal sights that you can barely believe exist.', -46.658473, -72.628423, 40, 8, 233333, 4.6, 0),
(128, 'Cliffs of Moher', 'Ireland', 'Ireland', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/2382681/pexels-photo-2382681.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'The Cliffs of Moher span 14 kilometers across County Clare, Ireland, and it’s a prime location for untamed, natural beauty.', 52.97257, -9.42938, 35, 9, 455555, 3.7, 0),
(129, 'Salar de Uyuni', 'Bolivia', 'Bolivia', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/13575545/pexels-photo-13575545.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'The Salar de Uyuni makes for an unusual trip, but it’s still one of the best vacations you might ever go on', -20.460369, -66.825832, 40, 6, 100000, 3.8, 0),
(130, 'Blue Lagoon', 'Iceland', 'Iceland', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/346972/pexels-photo-346972.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'If you’re a sucker for a good soak in a hot spring, the Blue Lagoon is one of the best places to travel.', 63.879083, -22.444951, 40, 4, 80000, 3.9, 0),
(131, 'Torres Del Paine National Park', 'Chile', 'Chile', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/66092/pexels-photo-66092.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1', 'The Torres Del Paine National Park is located in the southernmost region of the Andes, and it is full of diverse natural sights to enjoy.', -50.942357, -73.406718, 45, 3, 90000, 4.9, 0),
